videos.title: This Gravel Race Was Flooded | Dustman 2025
videos.description:
So I joined the 2025 UCI World Series Dustman in Kanchanaburi and boy was it flooded and extremely muddy. I think there were more than 10 river crossings as well as a lot of sticky and deep mud pools. Probably the toughest and most technical 130KM gravel race I've joined till date— but also the best cycling trip in a while. Did I make it? Enjoy!

videos.title: Dustman 130km Kanchanaburi | UCI Gravel World Series | 01.11.2025
videos.description:
1h 48 minutes of the Dustman race. I recorded until my battery died. Full race duration was 5h31m. Finished 7th place in my age group and qualified for Gravel World championships in 2026.  

Here's the ride on garmin:
https://connect.garmin.com/modern/activity/20855243812?share_unique_id=5
